Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Measurable
    Describes any class whose objects can measure other objects
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Helper class to calculate average and max value of a list of objects
    Parameters have to be from Measurable class
    Quiz
    Quiz that implements the Measurable interface.
    QuizRunner
    Program to receive a list of quizzes with scores and grade letters
    The output is the average from the list of quiz scores and the quiz with maximum score
    QuizTester
    Program to test the Quiz class using the Data class to calculate the average and maximum score
